how do i beat the big bug in zelda for the tear on the wii please help your best bet to keep yourself in the battle is to stay on one of the two larger rafts of wood that have a lot of stable ground next z target the giant insect and simply wait once he charges up and has purple bolts of electricity flashing around him he will likely charge at you when he does this jump to the side and into the water if you have to following this attack he will have a short cool down phase where he will be hanging down close to the water and not have his defense set up when he is doing this lunge at him and then bite by repeatedly hitting a once you get repulsed from him get onto one of the platforms of wood again and then repeat after three or so times of doing this he will fall over flipped over and exposing his weak point to deal massive damage jump onto his belly and charge up an energy field let loose to kill him http www gamefaqs com console wii file here is a walkthrough for the entire game good luck i'm about of the way through myself hope this helps The Legend of Zelda series enemies Items in the Metroid series GunZ The Duel Vehicles in Unreal Tournament 2004 Unreal Diablo II: Lord of Destruction Metroid Prime 2: Echoes Star Wars: Battlefront Super Metroid Natural Selection (computer game) Command & Conquer: Red Alert 2 GameFAQs New York Giants Metroid Prime The Legend of Zelda: Majora's Mask Half-Life GunBound Professional wrestling double-team maneuvers The Legend of Zelda: Ocarina of Time Halo 2 Bubble Bobble Protoss Sonic the Hedgehog (16-bit) Devil May Cry 3: Dante's Awakening Terminal ballistics Betting (poker) Tank Final Fantasy magic Pok__mon types Internal ballistics Dungeons & Dragons: Shadow over Mystara The Legend of Zelda: Twilight Princess Guilty Gear Terran (StarCraft) Combine (Half-Life 2) Professional wrestling throws USS Tunny (SS-282) Advance Wars: Dual Strike Lightning BZFlag Seismic retrofit Team Fortress Classic Professional wrestling attacks Sacrifice